lead_paragraph: It was classic Hillary Clinton, ignoring medical advice and attending a ceremony on a sultry New York City day while battling pneumonia - a decision ex-aides and other associates speculated was rooted in her longstanding desire to prove that women can compete in the male-dominated world of politics.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton's Overdrive Aimed at Breaking Women's Glass Ceiling
headline.print_headline: Hillary Clinton's Overdrive Aimed at Breaking Women's Glass Ceiling
